ca.sharcnet.nerve.docnav.dom

Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.sharcnet.nerve.docnav.dom.Attribute

  • public final class Attribute
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable key-value pair user by ElementNode. Two attributes are considered equal if key1=key2. Attributes are stored in an ElementNode using the AttributeList collection.
